reviewText: I bought this for someone's birthday and they couldn't be happier to see this series again.

please don't  permit  to be  riping off - the whole serie the transfer is NOT GOOD

and is not worst $ 26.99  - I got it  because I love to have the serie Dr. Casey

I've purchase  series and DVDs much older and  the copies  are perfect
For the price and the age of the series, I was very pleased with the overall quality of these dvds.

I remember when I was a kid my Mom watched this when it was in syndication (late 60's to early 70's)
Its too bad the few dvds available for Ben Casey are hard to find.
